  Memories and Compaction
  Configure shared memory and compaction defaults. Changes are saved to config

› [x] Use memories             Use memories in the following threads. Applied
                               at next thread.
  [ ] Generate memories        Generate memories from the following threads.
                               Current thread included.
  Compaction model and effort  Choose the shared model and reasoning used for
                               compact/refresh artifacts. Current: Current
                               thread model · current thread reasoning.
  Default compaction engine    Choose how /compact runs for all threads.
                               Current: Remote hybrid.
  Reset all memories           Clear local memory files and summaries.
                               Existing threads stay intact.

  Learn more: https://developers.openai.com/codex/memories

  Press enter to change or select
